roblems that arise Assist with audit requests Certified Public Accountant requirements This section should list the essential qualities of an ideal candidate. Include previous work experience, education or achievements that would be beneficial. And list any preferred hard and soft skills. Example Certified Public Accountant requirements Bachelor\u2019s degree in accounting and a CPA certification Minimum of 3 years experience in accounting roles High attention to detail and ability to spot mistakes or inconsistencies in financial documents Advanced knowledge of Microsoft Excel and accounting software Ability to remain organized and efficient when working under deadlines Superior communication skills and ability to provide excellent customer service Certified Public Accountant related job titles: Accountant Tax Accountant Senior Accountant Controller Senior Staff Accountant Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
